message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been valued at $15,000 by you. Considering its high quality and unique features, I believe we can come to an agreement that benefits both of us. To make this opportunity more appealing, I am offering it to you at a special introductory price of $14,000. This is a fantastic deal considering its market value and the benefits it offers. I look forward to your positive response.
